Java8 features
-----------------
1.Interface enhancement
2.Functional interface
3.Lambda expression
4.Stream API
6.Date Time API

------------------
Interface Enhancement

-Default methods were introduced, which helped to add new features without changing existing classes
hence enabling backward compatibility, also default methods gets accessed from implementing classes 

-- static methods are same as default but static methd dont get available for implements

Functional Interface(SAM) - Single Abstract Method
-------------------
Must have only 1 Abstract Method
Can have Static method
Can have default methods

-<Predicate Functional interface
-<Return boolean
